    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/korean-skincare-uk/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=559591673227641667&sectionId=559591673361859395)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSeD_5BpRe_text","label":"ggSeD_5BpRe_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gLdNijixX9\"><span style=\"color:#FFC5E1;\">Introduction</span></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtqxKFh4j_text","label":"ggRtqxKFh4j_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gDNtwsEfDx\">What is a facial mist and what is it for?</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDWYk8HtfY_text","label":"ggDWYk8HtfY_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gUD43H2Qtu\">What are the benefits of facial mists for your skin?</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUqM5Vr3_s_text","label":"ggUqM5Vr3_s_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gt-MbnaTNx\">How to choose the perfect facial mist for your skin type</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUmnVPmtOQ_text","label":"ggUmnVPmtOQ_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gedz2dV3ky\">Why choose Korean Skincare for your facial mists?</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYHNPE0oYQ_text","label":"ggYHNPE0oYQ_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gsOdbtIBlG\">Shop the recommended products</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA5hgLkFwW_text","label":"ggA5hgLkFwW_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#goUE24q9Y7\">Final thoughts</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsuc8uMOvV_text","label":"ggsuc8uMOvV_text","default":"<p><i>Hello, SkinTalks reader! Have you heard of facial mists but aren’t quite sure what they are or what they’re for? Don’t worry—we’ve got you covered!</i><br>&nbsp;</p><p><i>In this article, brought to you by Korean Skincare, we’ll clear up all your doubts about facial mists, their benefits, and what to consider when choosing the best mist for your skin type. Let’s dive in!</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoxIGOxvsy_text","label":"ggoxIGOxvsy_text","default":"What is a facial mist and what is it for?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGJGclMkS2_text","label":"ggGJGclMkS2_text","default":"<p>Let’s start with the basics: a <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/face-mists\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>facial mist</i></span></a> is a light, refreshing spray designed to hydrate and revitalize your skin. It’s like a quick boost of freshness you can use throughout the day or as part of your skincare routine.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>These little wonders are packed with amazing ingredients like hyaluronic acid, aloe vera, and plant extracts. Need extra hydration during the day? Want something to prep your skin before makeup? Facial mists are the answer!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Looking for something special? Check out our <a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/pyunkang-yul-mist-toner\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>Mist Toner by Pyunkang Yul</i></span></a>. Perfect for <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/sensitive-skin\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>sensitive skin</i></span></a>, it combines hydration with a calming effect. Super handy, right?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZASM0AhLB_text","label":"ggZASM0AhLB_text","default":"What are the benefits of facial mists for your skin?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggF94zXCbfL_text","label":"ggF94zXCbfL_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Facial mists are a multitasking product that works for every </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/blogs/skintalks/how-to-determine-your-skin-type\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>skin type</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">. Let’s explore their top benefits:</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcohb9YesS_text","label":"ggcohb9YesS_text","default":"1. Instant hydration"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNh_x9P0nP_text","label":"ggNh_x9P0nP_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Ever have days when your skin feels super dry and tired? Facial mists can fix that in seconds. Just keep it in your bag or on your desk for a quick and easy boost of hydration. Available in two portable sizes, the </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/haruharu-wonder-black-bamboo-mist\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>Black Bamboo Mist by Haruharu WONDER</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\"> is a nice addition to your to-go essentials.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg55aTFZsOj_text","label":"gg55aTFZsOj_text","default":"2. A calming effect"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjRMT-g1nJ_text","label":"ggjRMT-g1nJ_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Many facial mists are made with soothing ingredients like green tea or Centella Asiatica, which reduce </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/skin-redness\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>redness</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\"> and skin irritation. They’re a great choice for </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/sensitive-skin\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>sensitive</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\"> or </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/acne\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>acne-prone</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\"> skin. The </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/mixsoon-calming-boosting-mist\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>Calming Boosting Mist by Mixsoon</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\"> lives up to its name—it instantly soothes and hydrates delicate skin, delivering a refreshing boost of moisture.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggf9R-HgQNi_text","label":"ggf9R-HgQNi_text","default":"3. Environmental protection"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCyjnt1TK6_text","label":"ggCyjnt1TK6_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Did you know some mists also protect your skin from pollution and UV rays? These hydrating formulas help create a barrier that keeps your skin healthier. At Korean Skincare, we handpick the </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/face-mists\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>best facial mists</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\"> to ensure you always find the right product for your needs.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLww0IDH_M_text","label":"ggLww0IDH_M_text","default":"How to choose the perfect facial mist for your skin type"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAT0Jia7zK_text","label":"ggAT0Jia7zK_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Not sure where to start? Here are some quick tips to help you find the ideal facial mist for your </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/blogs/skintalks/how-to-determine-your-skin-type\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>skin type</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">:</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggz0eDWZjvB_text","label":"ggz0eDWZjvB_text","default":"Dry Skin"},{"type":"html","id":"ggh5JIGJ6fc_text","label":"ggh5JIGJ6fc_text","default":"<p>If you have <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/dry-skin\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>dry skin</i></span></a>, opt for a mist packed with hydration and nutrients, your skin will thank you! Our skincare specialist's own favorite is the <a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/rnw-der-special-ceramide-mist\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>RNW DER.SPECIAL Ceramide Mist</i></span></a><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>,</i></span> it contains 5 types of Ceramides that helps skin retain moisture, fortify its natural barrier and protects against visible damage from environmental stressors.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKc51h-wSJ_text","label":"ggKc51h-wSJ_text","default":"Oily or acne-prone skin"},{"type":"html","id":"ggo1BwhDlC0_text","label":"ggo1BwhDlC0_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">For </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/oily-skin\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>oily skin</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">, choose lightweight formulas with ingredients that control oil and soothe acne-prone skin. The </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/axis-y-dark-spot-correcting-glow-toner\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>AXIS-Y Dark Spot Correcting Glow Toner</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\"> is an ideal choice: it's &nbsp;a powerful yet gentle solution for brightening and balancing the skin, &nbsp;and a perfect companion to the bestselling Glow Serum.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdDmrduaem_text","label":"ggdDmrduaem_text","default":"Sensitive skin"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtLJ_Iy4bz_text","label":"ggtLJ_Iy4bz_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Avoid formulas with alcohol or fragrances and go for gentle products suitable for </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/sensitive-skin\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>sensitive skin</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">. A perfect fit is the </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/tiam-vita-b3-mist-toner\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>TIA'M Vita B3 Mist toner</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">: with its short ingredient list, it will brighten your skin and leave it feeling smooth and refreshed!</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMUNpCch3i_text","label":"ggMUNpCch3i_text","default":"Why choose Korean Skincare for your facial mists?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcTnLzcbR9_text","label":"ggcTnLzcbR9_text","default":"<p>At Korean Skincare, we take K-Beauty seriously! That’s why our selection includes top brands like <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/isntree\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>Isntree</i></span></a>, <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/missha\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>Missha</i></span></a>, and <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/pyunkang-yul\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>Pyunkang Yul</i></span></a>. We’re committed to ensuring you find high-quality products to care for your skin in the best way possible.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbTPRnZesm_text","label":"ggbTPRnZesm_text","default":"Shop the recommended products"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnaXxRJSbn_label","label":"ggnaXxRJSbn_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBUDU8DPsR_label","label":"ggBUDU8DPsR_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUqidPRwko_label","label":"ggUqidPRwko_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkrM3KHnO9_label","label":"ggkrM3KHnO9_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVnxirszl__label","label":"ggVnxirszl__label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3DmF0hoYb_label","label":"gg3DmF0hoYb_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBGWKX4pzx_text","label":"ggBGWKX4pzx_text","default":"Final thoughts"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRA4cODjof_text","label":"ggRA4cODjof_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Adding a </span><a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/face-mists\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#FD76A9;font-size:16px;\"><i>facial mist</i></span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\"> to your routine is a simple (but powerful!) way to care for your skin. You’ll enjoy extra hydration, a refreshing touch, and protection from daily stressors.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Explore our catalog and find the perfect facial mist for you—you’ll love the results, we promise!</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(35,35,35);font-size:16px;\">Take care, and see you next time!</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2ZJTbSou5_text","label":"gg2ZJTbSou5_text","default":"Keep reading Our SkinTalks"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_zg4PnUBV_label","label":"gg_zg4PnUBV_label","default":"<p>Read more</p>"}],
